            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Hd1e108">Rubrica 19</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De seueritate seu rigore: et crudelitate seu seuitia</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
      ¶ De seueritate seu rigore et 
               crude<lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>litate seu seuitia. Rubrica. 19
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e118">SEneca de clementia:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e125">Tam omnibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>ignoscere crudelitas est
        <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>est quam nulli medium tenere debemus <!--146.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>Uoluntas oportet ante seuiendi quam causa 
               defici<lb ed="#V" n="48" break="no"/>at. Alioquin quemadmodum prescisse arbores
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>plurimis ramis repullulant. Ita regia 
               crude<lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>litas auget inmicorum numerum tollendo: 
               paren<lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>tes enim liberique eorum qui interfecti sunt et 
               pro<lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>pinqui et amici in locum singulorum succedunt.
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>Tyranni in voluntate seuiunt: reges non nisi ex
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>causa ac necessitate. Clementie contrariam 
               impe<lb ed="#V" n="55" break="no"/>riti putant seueritatem: sed nulla virtus virtuti
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>contraria est. Quid ergo opponitur clementie
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>crudelitas: que nihil aliud quam attrocitas animi
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>in penis exigendis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e163">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e162">Seneca in prouerb.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e167">Respue crudelitatem et
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>matrem crudelitatis iram.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e174">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e175">Lucanus li. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e178">Facere omnia seue
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>Non impune licet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e184">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e187">Ualerius maximus li. 6. tit. de seueritate.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e188">Cambises mali cuiusdam iudicis e corpore
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>pellende tractam selle intendi in: eaque filium
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>eius iudicaturum considere iussit. Ceterum
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>et rex et barbarus attroci ac noua pena 
               iudi<lb ed="#V" n="68" break="no"/>cis ne quis postea corumumpi iudex posset 
               pro<lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>uidit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e205"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e206">Libro. 9. ti. de crudelitate:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e207">Seuus
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>fuit enei thauri inuentor: quo inclusi 
               subdi<lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>tis ignibus longo et abdito cruciatu mugitus
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>resonantes spiritum edere cogebantur: ne 
               eiula<lb ed="#V" n="73" break="no"/>tus eorum humano sono vocis expraessi 
               phaleri<lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>dis tyranni misericordiam implorare possent:
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>quam quia calamitosis deesse voluit teterminum
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>artis sue opus primus inclusus merito 
               au<lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>spicatus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e228">
               <lb ed="#V" n="78"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e233">Auctor libri de formula honeste vite. c. 4</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e232">Seuerior esto iudicio quam sermone: vita quam
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>vultu: vltor clemens: seuitie detestator.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e240">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e246">Cassiodorus epistolarum libro. 11. et pe.
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>epistola. 41. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e244">Qui iustitie inexorabili 
               ex<lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>cubat: necesse est vt eum pietas benigna 
               de<lb ed="#V" n="84" break="no"/>sinat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e254">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e263">Gregorius in pastorali. ca. 18</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e258">Disciplina
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>vel misericordia multum destituitur si vna 
               si<lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>ne altera teneatur. Sed erga subditos suos
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>inesse rectoribus debet: tunc iuste consulens
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>misericordia et pie seuiens disciplina.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-d1e271">
               <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Rd1e282">Gaufridus in poetria. c. 94.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45498-Qd1e275">Cum possis 
               no<lb ed="#V" n="91" break="no"/>li seuire: memento neronis.</quote> <!--147.xml-->
            </p>
